          <text><![CDATA[<p> <strong>21st Century Automated Vehicle Safety Act of 2018</strong></p> <p> This bill directs the Department of Transportation to make grants on a competitive basis to eligible entities (i.e., nonprofit organizations, states and localities, and institutions of higher education) for such entities to establish pilot programs to advance high-definition road mapping in order to further the safe deployment of highly automated vehicles.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-06-08T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
